Title: Young Man With a Horn
Plot: A popular young singer is found dead outside an infamous Las Vegas nightclub, leading the CSI team to uncover a link between that crime and a murder 50 years earlier.
ParentalRatingReason: R16 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Archie Kao, Tippi Hedren, Robert Guillaume, Larry Mitchell, Tiffany Hines, Benjamin Bledsoe, Holt McCallany, Seamus Deaver, Bill Cobbs, Ralph Waite
